title: Mr. Seth V. (Dad)
text: I hate dragging out negotiating cost for something that has no menu with prices! with Victory they called me and said "I can't charge you the amount we contracted?" Victory not only was honest lawyer business; but gave me one bad news and two good news Quote: s? "I chose bad first" "In realty all three; was better news for my family and myself." Victory shared the same cocern I would have at a IRS negotiating table...."if I knew how." Victory the name say's it all!!! I recommend Victory to all who need true help with honesty!
